title: Shutdown could reduce US flights 'to a trickle', transport secretary warns
description: US lawmakers are working over the weekend as they seek a bipartisan deal to end the shutdown, which is now on day 40.
content:
Flight delays and cancellations continue to snarl US air travel for a third day as Transportation Secretary Sean Duffy warned air traffic will be "reduced to a trickle" if the US government shutdown continues.
